# Demo Instructions

Use this profile as a demonstration model for safe, general-purpose repository work. Start with MCP context and context packs before broad source reads.

Treat generated code, public interfaces, legacy interop, configuration, and build scripts as high-risk areas. Do not read secrets. Do not run app servers, Docker, migrations, SQL, or database commands unless explicitly approved.
